"title": "6702: peace, human destruction of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6702",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Because of human sinfulness, God's provision of peace is always under threat. Scripture shows that this breaking of peace has implications for the whole of creation.</p>\n<h2>Causes of the destruction of peace</h2>\n<h3>Sin and self-centredness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:21\">ISA 57:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen11:4-Gen11:9\">GEN 11:4–11:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:7-Isa59:8\">ISA 59:7–59:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:41-Luke19:44\">LUK 19:41–19:44</a></p>\n<h3>Idolatry</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech10:2\">ZEC 10:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:7-Exod32:10\">EXO 32:7–32:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:9-1Tim6:10\">1TI 6:9–6:10</a></p>\n<h3>Fear and anxiety</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:19\">JHN 20:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:3-Josh7:5\">JOS 7:3–7:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:25\">PRO 29:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer30:10\">JER 30:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer46:27\">JER 46:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:31-Matt6:34\">MAT 6:31–6:34</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:29-Luke12:30\">LUK 12:29–12:30</a></p>\n<h3>The sins of ancestors</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:36-Lev26:42\">LEV 26:36–26:42</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:16-Gen3:19\">GEN 3:16–3:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:26-2Kgs23:27\">2KI 23:26–23:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:29\">JER 31:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek18:2\">EZK 18:2</a></p>\n<h3>Friends</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer20:10\">JER 20:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam1:1-Lam1:2\">LAM 1:1–1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam1:19\">LAM 1:19</a></p>\n<h3>Enemies</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:19-Ps35:20\">PSA 35:19–35:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs9:14-2Kgs9:28\">2KI 9:14–9:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam1:16\">LAM 1:16</a></p>\n<h2>The consequences of the human destruction of peace</h2>\n<h3>Humanity suffers</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:53-Deut28:57\">DEU 28:53–28:57</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs2:5-1Kgs2:6\">1KI 2:5–2:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:24-2Kgs6:29\">2KI 6:24–6:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:2-2Kgs25:3\">2KI 25:2–25:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek13:10-Ezek13:16\">EZK 13:10–13:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:3-Rev6:8\">REV 6:3–6:8</a></p>\n<h3>Nations suffer</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:31-Jer49:32\">JER 49:31–49:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek38:14-Ezek38:23\">EZK 38:14–38:23</a></p>\n<h3>The land suffers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer25:37\">JER 25:37</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod8:12-Exod8:14\">EXO 8:12–8:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:27-Lev26:35\">LEV 26:27–26:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:7\">ISA 1:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa36:16-Isa36:20\">ISA 36:16–36:20</a></p>\n<h3>The whole creation suffers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:3-Rev6:4\">REV 6:3–6:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:5-Gen6:7\">GEN 6:5–6:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa24:1-Isa24:5\">ISA 24:1–24:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:22\">ROM 8:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev8:7-Rev8:13\">REV 8:7–8:13</a></p>",
